{"title":"ubuntu改密钥登录与时区时间","uid":"c070e94dae14088f5f79d1b076658719","slug":"ubuntu-keylogin-time","date":"2022-12-28T09:54:59.000Z","updated":"2022-12-28T06:31:22.249Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ubuntu-keylogin-time.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<center>\n\n<p><img src=\"/images/202212/ubuntu.png\" alt=\"Ubuntu\"></p>\n</center>\n\n<h2 id=\"一、改密钥登录\"><a href=\"#一、改密钥登录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、改密钥登录\"></a>一、改密钥登录</h2><h3 id=\"1-authorized-keys上传到服务器某个用户的-x2F-ssh目录下\"><a href=\"#1-authorized-keys上传到服务器某个用户的-x2F-ssh目录下\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.authorized_keys上传到服务器某个用户的~&#x2F;.ssh目录下\"></a>1.authorized_keys上传到服务器某个用户的~&#x2F;.ssh目录下</h3><h3 id=\"2-修改服务器ssh配置\"><a href=\"#2-修改服务器ssh配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.修改服务器ssh配置\"></a>2.修改服务器ssh配置</h3><p>进入ssh的配置文件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>进行如下配置：</strong></p>\n<p>去掉注释</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">AuthorizedKeysFile %h/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>禁用root登录 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">PermitRootLogin no</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>禁用密码登录 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">PasswordAuthentication no</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-重新启动\"><a href=\"#3-重新启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.重新启动\"></a>3.重新启动</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service ssh restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"二、修改ubuntu时区时间\"><a href=\"#二、修改ubuntu时区时间\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、修改ubuntu时区时间\"></a>二、修改ubuntu时区时间</h2><h3 id=\"安装ntpdate\"><a href=\"#安装ntpdate\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装ntpdate\"></a>安装ntpdate</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install ntpdate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>首先查看时区： </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">date</span> -R</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果要修改时区，执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo tzselect</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>复制文件到&#x2F;etc目录下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">cp</span> /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai  /etc/localtime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"更新时间\"><a href=\"#更新时间\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新时间\"></a>更新时间</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo ntpdate time.windows.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","feature":true,"text":" 一、改密钥登录1.authorized_keys上传到服务器某个用户的~&#x2F;.ssh目录下2.修改服务器ssh配置进入ssh的配置文件： 1vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config 进行如下配置： 去掉注释 1AuthorizedKeysFile %h/.ssh...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":470,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."